<div class="ui accordion">
    <div class="active title">
        <i class="dropdown icon"></i>
        What are the rules?
    </div>
    <div class="active content">
        <p>There is a single rule: please show up on time or cancel yourself before the assignment, otherwise you will be <u>banned</u>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="title">
        <i class="dropdown icon"></i>
        Where are the assignment locations?
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Meeting points will be drawn from this list:</p>
        <ul>
            {{# each locations}}
                <li>{{ this.name }} <small>({{ this.details }}, <a href="{{ this.plan }}">plan</a>)</small></li>
            {{/each}}
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="title">
        <i class="dropdown icon"></i>
        How do I find my lunch mates?
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Usually people standing and looking around at the same point are easy to spot. You can as well put one hand on your stomach as a discrete rallying sign. However make sure to be at the good location by checking the corresponding plan.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="title">
        <i class="dropdown icon"></i>
        Can I bring a friend/colleague with me?
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Sure! However, please limit to a single friend/colleague as you already know each other and finding a table for more than 5-6 people might be tricky.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="title">
        <i class="dropdown icon"></i>
        How can I avoid fear of silence?
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>There are plenty of interesting topics to discuss, beyond the traditional small talk (name, origin, hobbies, ...). Ask about past experiences, current projects or brainstorm together about an issue!</p>
    </div>
</div>

